details.biography: Ali Keshavji, or "Ali Kesh" as he prefers to be known, lives in London,  England, where he works for a small video production firm. He is  currently completing work on "True Fan," a documentary about the world  of Star Wars fandom akin to the "Trekkies" series on Star Trek fandom.  He had a cameo in the most recent Star Wars installment, Revenge of the  Sith.
